SMTP
  Simple Mail Transfer Protocol

Port No is 25.
Port No of IMAP(Internet Message Access Protocol) is 143.
Port No of POP3(Post Office Protocol v3) is 110.

Postfix is the application used to configure SMTP, for sending and receiving mails(without attachments).

When any mail is sent, it follows 4 basic steps,
    i) Mail User Agents(MUA)-   Mail is sent from Client(You.gmail) to server(Gmail, Yahoo, etc).
    ii) Mail Submission Agents(MSA)-    Mail is sent from the Server1(Gmail) to Server2(Gmail/Yahoo).
    iii) Mail Transmission Agents(MTA)- Mail is sent from the Server2(Yahoo) to Client(xyz.yahoo).
    iv) Mail Delivery Agents(MDA)

